Europe map, start of 1941

Eric Rauchway

7/17/2022

Map draws from Natural Earth datasets and also from Michael de Groots Building the New Order as well as the Rand-McNally map of Africa in 1939, from the David Rumsey Map Collection. Color palette adapted from CARTOcolors. Made using R with ggplot and sf, as well as some use of QGIS. With gratitude especially to Kieran Healy.
